   ```

3. **Push + PR:**
   ```bash
   git push origin task/{task-slug}
   gh pr create --title "[Task-Titel]" --body "[Beschreibung]"
   ```

4. **PR-URL als Deliverable registrieren:**
   ```
   POST /api/v1/agent/me/deliverable
